title: Camden County Bike Crashes, 2008-2010 - Map 4
name: Camden County Bike Crashes, 2008-2010 - Map 4
description:
Crash locations are described by the street and cross street (when given) provided in NJDOT&apos;s Crash Records. Crash locations are mapped by the street and cross street or latitude and longitude given in NJDOT&apos;s Crash Records. When a crash occurred in a block and longitude and latitude were not provided, mileposts were used to find the location of the crash, when possible.
All crashes are bicyclist-vehicle. All locations are approximate. 
Data source: NJ DOT Crash Records reporting system, 2008-2010.
